Paper: hep-th/9410227

Date: 1994-10-29

Title: Distance Formula for Grassmann Manifold --Applied to Anandan--Aharonov

Type Uncertainty Relation--Authors: Minoru Hirayama, Takeshi Hamada and Jin Chen

Comments: 25pages, LaTex file , TOYAMA-80, KANAZAWA-94-21

Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 93 (1995) 255-272

The time-energy uncertainty relation of Anandan-Aharonov is generalized to arelation involving a set of quantum state vectors. This is achieved byobtaining an explicit formula for the distance between two finitely separatedpoints in the Grassmann manifold.